headline: Down 23% This Year, Is It Finally Time to Buy Nike Stock?
summary: Nike has experienced a slowdown in sales, and investors are worried about new tariffs.  Nike stock is down, but it's not as cheap as you might think.  Nike (NYSE: NKE) is the largest athletic apparel company in the world, by far.
